---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'; 
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | 2 Smokin' Barrels">
    <main class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 2.5rem; background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-radius: 16px; backdrop-filter: blur(12px);">
        <h1 class="page-title" style="font-family: 'Mr Dafoe', cursive; font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--accent-pink); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(234, 72, 178, 0.6);">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p style="color: var(--white-med); text-align: center;"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> May 10, 2026</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">By accessing 2smokinbarrels.com and utilizing the Command Center, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the interactive features of this site[cite: 19].</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">2. Description of Service</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">2 Smokin' Barrels provides interactive web tools ("Command Center") that allow viewers to trigger actions, overlays, and events on a live broadcast via a secure WebSocket connection to Streamer.bot[cite: 19].</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">3. User Conduct</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">You agree to use the Command Center responsibly. You shall not[cite: 19]:</p>
        <ul style="color: var(--white-med); padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
            <li>Use automated scripts, bots, or auto-clickers to spam the Command Center[cite: 19].</li>
            <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, exploit, or bypass the point costs associated with stream actions[cite: 19].</li>
            <li>Use the service to transmit malicious code, payloads, or unauthorized WebSocket requests[cite: 19].</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">4. Account Access and Termination</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">Access to the Command Center is a privilege. We reserve the right to ban, block, or revoke any user's access at our sole discretion, without notice, for abusive behavior or violation of these terms[cite: 19].</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">5. Limitation of Liability</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">The tools and services on this website are provided "as is" and "as available." 2 Smokin' Barrels makes no warranties regarding the continuous availability of the Command Center[cite: 19].</p>

        <h3 style="font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--accent-orange); margin-top: 2rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">6. Third-Party Services</h3>
        <p style="color: var(--white-low);">Our website utilizes third-party services including Google, Cloudflare, and YouTube. Your use of these features is also subject to the respective terms of service of those platforms, including the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/t/terms" style="color: var(--accent-pink); text-decoration: underline;">YouTube Terms of Service</a>[cite: 19].</p>
    </main>
</Layout>